title: Fear is Not the Boss of You (Ft. Jennifer Allwood)
description:
Have trials or your past experiences left you feeling afraid of the future?

You are not the only one.

In this episode, Jordan has an honest and candid conversation about tackling some of our biggest, or simply most nagging, fears with Jennifer Allwood, author of Fear is Not the Boss of You.

When it comes to pursuing your greatest dreams, tune in to learn practical steps you can take to feel the fear and do it anyway.
author: matt@jordanleedooley.com (Jordan Lee Dooley)
